data.title: Map of Berlin commuter rail (s bahn): stations & lines
data.meta_description: Printable & PDF maps of Berlin commuter rail, urban rail & suburban train (s bahn) with informations about the Deutsche Bahn network map, the stations and the 15 lines & routes.
data.text: You can find on this page the map of Berlin suburban train. The Berlin s bahn, urban, suburban & communter train is a transit system serving the city of Berlin (Germany) with the subway, the tram, the bus or the ferry. The commuter train network has 15 lines and 166 stations forming a rail network of 205 miles (331 km).
